msgid ""
"To determine if MongoDB used index intersection, run "
":method:`~cursor.explain()`; the results of :ref:`explain() <explain-"
"output-index-intersection>` will include either an ``AND_SORTED`` stage "
"or an ``AND_HASH`` stage."
